    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine, it has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and timing integrity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission to an M Variable Differential Lock, providing unparalleled analog feedback. The chassis is exceptionally tight, benefiting from a recent suspension refresh using OEM bushings. With original paint, matching VIN tags on all panels, and a documented service pedigree, this vehicle represents a turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
