    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available now is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with a mirror-like finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of wear, bolster compression, or creasing. All interior surfaces, including the wood trim and dashboard, are flawless, and every electronic feature\u2014from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a full folder of maintenance records to prove it. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the car drives with the tight, responsive feel of a brand-new vehicle. This sale includes two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and all owner's manuals. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is the one.",
